title: Egyptian records in Olympic weightlifting
text: The following are the records of <a href="Egypt">Egypt</a> in <a href="Olympic%20weightlifting">Olympic weightlifting</a>. Records are maintained in each <a href="weight%20class">weight class</a> for the <a href="snatch%20%28weightlifting%29">snatch</a> lift, <a href="clean%20and%20jerk">clean and jerk</a> lift, and the total for both lifts by the <a href="Egyptian%20Weightlifting%20Federation">Egyptian Weightlifting Federation</a>.
